      <title>8bitdo 藍芽轉接器</title>
      <link>https://blog.deverqqqq.dev/posts/2021/8bitdo-%E8%97%8D%E8%8A%BD%E8%BD%89%E6%8E%A5%E5%99%A8/</link>
